### Contexts API Test Suite (RAG System)
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000/contexts
### Auth: Bearer token required (Clerk JWT)

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = your_clerk_jwt_token_here
@contextId = replace_with_actual_context_id
@entryId = replace_with_actual_entry_id

### 1. Create context base
POST {{baseUrl}}/contexts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Brand Voice - Tech Startup",
  "description": "Our brand guidelines, voice, and successful content patterns",
  "type": "brand_voice",
  "settings": {
    "autoIndexNewContent": true,
    "maxEntries": 1000,
    "similarityThreshold": 0.7
  }
}

### 2. List context bases (with filters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/contexts?type=brand_voice&isActive=true&search=tech
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get context base by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/contexts/{{contextId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Update context base
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/contexts/{{contextId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated brand voice with new guidelines",
  "settings": {
    "maxEntries": 2000
  }
}

### 5. Delete context base
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/contexts/{{contextId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Add entry to context base
POST {{baseUrl}}/contexts/{{contextId}}/entries
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "We use bold, modern language. We're enthusiastic about technology but never overly technical. Our target audience is 25-40 year old professionals who value efficiency and innovation.",
  "metadata": {
    "source": "brand-guidelines",
    "category": "tone",
    "dateAdded": "2025-10-08"
  }
}

### 7. Remove entry from context base
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/contexts/{{contextId}}/entries/{{entryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Auto-create from social account (THE MAGIC!)
POST {{baseUrl}}/contexts/autocreate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "platform": "instagram",
  "brandId": "your_instagram_account_id",
  "analysisDepth": "full",
  "includeEngagementMetrics": true
}

### 9. Enhance prompt with RAG (THE REAL MAGIC! 🔥)
POST {{baseUrl}}/contexts/enhance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Create a product launch video",
  "contentType": "video",
  "contextBaseIds": ["{{contextId}}"],
  "useBrandVoice": true,
  "useContentLibrary": true,
  "useAudience": true,
  "maxContextEntries": 5
}

### 10. Query context base (semantic search)
POST {{baseUrl}}/contexts/query
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contextBaseIds": ["{{contextId}}"],
  "query": "What's our brand's tone of voice?",
  "limit": 3
}

### 11. Get context base stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/contexts/{{contextId}}/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Example: Full RAG workflow
### Step 1: Create brand voice context
# @name createBrandContext
POST {{baseUrl}}/contexts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My Brand Voice",
  "description": "Company brand guidelines and successful content",
  "type": "brand_voice"
}

### Step 2: Add brand guidelines
@brandContextId = {{createBrandContext.response.body._id}}

POST {{baseUrl}}/contexts/{{brandContextId}}/entries
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Brand Guidelines: We're a modern tech company. Use conversational tone. Target audience: 25-40 professionals. Colors: Blue (#0066FF) and Cyan (#00CCFF). Always be enthusiastic but professional.",
  "metadata": {
    "source": "brand-guidelines",
    "category": "identity"
  }
}

### Step 3: Use RAG to enhance prompt
POST {{baseUrl}}/contexts/enhance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Create a video about our new feature",
  "contentType": "video",
  "contextBaseIds": ["{{brandContextId}}"],
  "useBrandVoice": true
}

### Response will be:
### {
###   "originalPrompt": "Create a video about our new feature",
###   "enhancedPrompt": "Create a modern, professional video about our new feature targeting 25-40 year old professionals. Use conversational but enthusiastic tone. Include our brand colors blue (#0066FF) and cyan (#00CCFF). Keep it engaging and showcase innovation.",
###   "context": [
###     {
###       "content": "Brand Guidelines: We're a modern tech company...",
###       "source": "My Brand Voice",
###       "relevance": 0.92
###     }
###   ],
###   "estimatedQualityBoost": 46
### }


